Self-acclaimed ‘Africa’s certified relationship/mental expert, Blessing Okoro Nkiruka aka Blessing CEO has offered an insight into why most men are still married. The controversial self-styled ‘intellectual entertainer’ in a 16-second video shared on her Instagram page argued many men are still married because they have side chicks who fill the gap pending when they solve issues with their spouses. “Side chicks are one of the major reasons a lot of men still stay married. When their cars break down, they have spare tyre to manage until the fix their main tyre,” she said.   Mummy G.O. in Dubai     Pastor Ibiyeomie to police: If you take bribes from ‘yahoo…     Oyo Senator Teslim Folarin loses wife   The divorced relationship adviser ended her short speech by asking“Imagine there were no spare tyres.” - Advertisement - Blessing CEO captioned The video: “Side chicks are one of the Major reasons a lot of men still stay married…Focus on your marriages leave the noise outside. “Married women and yet to be married Ladies you don’t want to miss this. If you like stay in my comment session and (be) fighting your keypad. “If you drop ur phones reality will show you…learn.”